{"tid":1768581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港航空公司訓練空姐學詠春以應對失控“空怒族”引爭議！","createTime":"2019-12-04T07:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T02:38:49.000Z","uid":297241,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"32fbd99d7457ef7ab90d95fdfda1c13320816a03","tid":1768581,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"空姐學習詠春拳應對「不規矩」的乘客<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一家航空公司為全體空乘人員開設培訓課程，學習詠春拳。受過詠春拳的空姐表示，中途不知道會發生什麼，學習詠春拳之後，就可以保護自己，增強安全感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d.blog.xuite.net/d/8/4/1/24075001/blog_2321935/txt/83269282/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd.blog.xuite.net%2Fd%2F8%2F4%2F1%2F24075001%2Fblog_2321935%2Ftxt%2F83269282%2F1.jpg&h=7de4865d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.westca.com/uploads/201308/0000000266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.westca.com%2Fuploads%2F201308%2F0000000266.jpg&h=af30f3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.westca.com/uploads/201308/0000000550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.westca.com%2Fuploads%2F201308%2F0000000550.jpg&h=b20eddc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.westca.com/uploads/201308/00000001101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.westca.com%2Fuploads%2F201308%2F00000001101.jpg&h=b133ddfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.westca.com/uploads/201308/0000000841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.westca.com%2Fuploads%2F201308%2F0000000841.jpg&h=9c2142ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.westca.com/uploads/201308/0000001140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.westca.com%2Fuploads%2F201308%2F0000001140.jpg&h=6d10b63f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d04f580341f50417bd94d95ec00f2450e812d53","tid":1768581,"uid":164240,"like